<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828603>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Male of Anisophlugis appendicula (Gorochov, 2015) n. comb. A – B habituS, (A) lateral view, (B) dorSal view. (C) head in frontal view. D – E head and pronotum, (D) lateral view, (E) dorSal view. F – G fore legS, (F) inner face, (G) outer face. H – I tegmina in dorSal view, (H) right, (I) left. Red arrow indicateS tympanum" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828603/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828605>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Female of Anisophlugis appendicula (Gorochov, 2015) n. comb. A – B habituS, (A) lateral view, (B) dorSal view. (C) head in frontal view. D – E head and pronotum, (D) lateral view, (E) dorSal view. (F) apex of abdomen in ventral view. (G) drawing of Subgenital plate in ventral view. H – I apex of abdomen, (H) dorSal view, (I) lateral view. Red arrow indicateS Subgenital plate with appendix." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828605/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.828607>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Male of Anisophlugis appendicula (Gorochov, 2015) n. comb. (A) cercuS lateral view. B – D apex of abdomen, (B) axial view, (C) dorSal view, (D) ventral view. E – F Stridulatory fileS, (E) right, (F) left. Black arrow indicateS epiproct, red arrow indicateS paraproctS, * indicateS Subgenital plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/828607/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

